text: Pauline Ranvier (born 14 April 1994) is a French foil fencer. At the 2019 World Fencing Championships, she won the silver medal in the foil tournament. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Paris Category:French female fencers Category:French foil fencers
